POE2GPS — a strictly read-only Path of Exile 2 navigation overlay.

Derived from Sikaka/POE2Radar (MIT License) with the process-randomization layer
adapted from NattKh/POE2Radar (MIT License). The auto-flask keystroke feature and
all poe.ninja/poe2scout economy network calls have been removed; POE2GPS reads game
memory only and never sends input to or writes into the game process.

